<div id="text-block-511a3784ba0abb364a1bad56faa91812" class="sh-text-block">
	<p style="text-align: center;">Our Community Calendar is a free service to the art community for posting art events.  As a Non-Profit, we do not post  political or religious content, only art content to build the creative community and support artists.</p></div>

<div id="button-6009a8c4ee0fa95fd1b3130a4bf0029c" class="sh-button-container  sh-button-style-1 sh-animated bounce"data-wow-duration="2s">
	<div class="sh-element-margin">
		<a href="https://evanstonmade.org/calendar/community/add/" target="_self" class="sh-button sh-button-xlarge ">

			
							<span class="sh-button-text">
					Submit Your Events!				</span>
			
			
		</a>
			</div>
</div>

